{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/storing-values-with-the-assignment-operator","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Cuvanje Vrednosti Pomocu Operatera Dodele","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U JavaScript-u mozete cuvati vrednost u promenljivoj koristeci <dfn>operater dodele</dfn> (<code>=</code>).</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">myVariable = 5;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ovo dodeljuje broj <code>5</code> promenljivoj <code>myVariable</code>.</p>\n<p>Ako postoji bilo kakva racunica sa desne strane operatera <code>=</code>, ona se izvrsi pre nego sto se vrednost dodeli promenljivoj sa leve strane.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">var myVar;\nmyVar = 5;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Prvo, ovaj kod kreira promenljivu <code>myVar</code>. Zatim kod dodeljuje <code>5</code> promenljivoj <code>myVar</code>. Ako se <code>myVar</code> ponovo pojavi u kodu, program ce je tretirati kao da je <code>5</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244a8","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Dodelite vrednost <code>7</code> promenljivoj <code>a</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18310,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/storing-values-with-the-assignment-operator"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Setup\nvar a;\n\n// Only change code below this line","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Ne treba da menjate kod iznad navedenog komentara.</p>","testStrin